Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory259.png'}
{3: 'Although the Queen Program has been defeated, she does not seem to have taken any damage. You barely see a scratch on her.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Queen Program', 3: 'Your ridiculous struggle<//TRICK> will not prevail—this is my domain! I am its soverign<//ADMINISTRATOR>!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'The Queen Program raises her hand, and Lucia and the group are all frozen. Not only can they not pick up their weapons, they cannot even move a single step.'}
{2: 'Bugged Bunny', 3: 'Freeze<//DUMMY>! Freeze<//DUMMY>!'}
{3: 'Following a furious roar, a cannonball explodes next to the Queen Program, and the dust and smoke cloud her vision.'}
{3: "Inside the chaos, a hand grabs onto Nanami's arm and drags her out of the smoke."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Karenina?! What are you doing here?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "Why do you think, you dummy?! I'm here to save you!", 4: '2'}
{3: "Nanami shakes Karenina's hand off hers and stubbornly turns away."}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "That's impossible! You're lying! Nanami won't be tricked that easily!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Everyone thinks Nanami is annoying! Everyone thinks I am trouble! Why... why would anyone wants Nanami back?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Queen Program', 3: 'Return Nanami<//#%?#%?> to me! She is my necessary tool<//KEY>!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'The Queen Program rushes toward the two of them, but as her hand is about to reach Nanami, a bullet hits her right in the arm.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Nanami is Nanami... She's not yours...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv, hold her back!'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "Roger! You won't move any closer to her!", 4: '1'}
{3: "Liv's Levi-Gun and Lee's pistols create a dense field of cover fire, forcing the Queen Program back."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Queen Program', 3: 'That is impossible... Why can you move?! Wait—where are the other two?!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Chrome! Lucia!', 3: '37'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiHitNew.prefab', 2: '2'}
{3: 'Two sharp blades strike at the Queen Program from her blindsides, sending her flying.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'The slashing movement feels way worse in the virtual space. Huh.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Commandant, Liv and you should take Nanami to a safe area. Leave this to us.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Alright, got it.', 3: '45'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory260.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "Liv... weren't you angry because of Nanami's April Fools pranks?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "I'm so sorry, Nanami... Because of the anomaly, everything we said back then came out opposite of what we actually meant.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Even when Nanami replaced the matcha powder with wasabi powder in the dessert you made for Commandant?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Uh... That... should be alright?', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "So, all of you are still Nanami's friends...?", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Nanami turns to look at the annoyed Karenina, seemingly waiting for her answer specifically.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'You idiot... Who will stop caring for you just because of a prank or two?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'So... that program tricked me?!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Karenina cannot help but laugh.'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "Hahahaha! That's splendid! That's probably karma, and you probably deserved it!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'How did you find us here, Karenina?', 3: '67'}
{3: 'Karenina scratches her head, slightly embarrassed.'}

{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'When Nanami came to the Engineering Force and informed us about this, I was really angry... But then I calmed down and did some digging, and I did find some traces of suspicious programs...', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'See! Nanami told you so!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "Fine, fine... I'm sorry I screwed up...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "What was that? I can't hear you!", 4: '1'}

{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Enough with it... Because I was prepared, the Engineering Force managed to connect with Gestalt and came up with a solution when I was dragged to the virtual space, and we executed emergency repairs.', 4: '2'}
{2: "So that's how the malfunction on Liv and everyone was fixed...", 3: '76'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Then... what would happen to these abnormal programs...?', 4: '1'}

{2: 'Karenina', 3: "The temporary solution is to isolate them from the anomaly. They are results from a bug in Gestalt, after all, so it's up to the Science Council and the folks upstairs eventually.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "It's starting...", 4: '2'}
{3: 'A giant ebony crack appears behind the Queen Program, and all the abnormal programs are sucked inside.'}
{2: "Is that Gestalt's isolated drive?", 3: '81'}
{2: 'Queen Program', 3: 'Our kingdom<//UTOPIA>... Freedom<//LIES>...'}
{3: "Half of the Queen Program's body is buried with the crack, but her hands are still grabbing on to the ground outside, refusing to let go."}
{2: 'Karenina, your body!', 3: '86'}
{3: "Karenina's body slowly turns translucent—as well as Liv beside her."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "We were dragged here by that giant woman there, and now that she's defeated, I think we're being sent back.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "But then, those of us who're fighting the Queen are also...", 4: '2'}
{3: 'Indeed, both Lucia and Lee are almost completely gone, significantly weakening the attacks that hold the Queen Program back, giving her a moment of respite.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Nanami... is coming to help!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Hey, hold on!', 4: '2'}
{3: "Ignoring Karenina's cry, Nanami picks up her chainsaw and charges at the Queen Program."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: "Nanami, what are you doing?! Get out of there! It's dangerous!", 4: '1'}
{3: "Her chainsaw comes down on the Queen Program's arm, and the Queen Program sinks deeper into the crack behind the beautiful, metal-clashing sparks."}
{3: "Seeing the Queen Program's expression, Nanami frowns, but her face is filled with pity."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'You were born from an error, and so you wanted to create a world of falsehoods and mistakes.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "But you shouldn't have attacked those who don't approve of you. You should never take advantage of other people's kindness.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'People make mistakes... but people also reflect and change. So... go reflect on yours!', 4: '1'}

{3: "Nanami's chainsaw digs deep into the ground, and with a thunderous crack, a large piece of the floor is broken off. The spots that the Queen Program is holding on crumple, and soon she is entirely devoured by the crack."}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Maybe when we see each other again...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'As the crack closes, the storm of data stream slowly dies down, leaving Nanami by herself in the empty square.'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "You can truly become Nanami's friends...", 4: '1'}
